      "side": 1,
      "message": "why is this needed? this means that if someone is looking at the canary graph in go/buildbucket-dashboard and sees that everything seems fine, they might incorrectly conclude that canary packages wai, while in reality they aren\u0027t even used.",
      "revId": "c60d300046f10b58a1d066d4947b5fd0eb7a3810",
