      "writtenOn": "2020-05-29T18:23:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "i think i was not very clear.\n\ntoday we rely on metrics with canary\u003dtrue. For example, we can narrow down to (canary\u003dtrue, builder\u003dX), see that such builds exist and conclude that canary is working for them. This knob enable users to lie about canary: the canary would be true, but nothing is being actually canaryed.\n\n---------\n\nalso i still don\u0027t understand why this is needd",
