      "writtenOn": "2020-05-29T18:54:14Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ok, these are legitimate concerns.\n\nI was trying to capture being able to opt-in/opt-out of \"experiments\".\n\nWhat if instead of a new message, we instead had a permanent field\n\n   map\u003cstring, Trinary\u003e canary_experiments\n\nAnd document which experiment keys currently do which things?\n\nI would only add \"use_bbagent\" there for now, but we could also use this field for other experiments.",
      "parentUuid": "b604cbfb_68bb4b52",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 466,
